        {
            "title": "立足股壇｜港股值博率不高 資金未轉樂觀｜JK爸爸（陳立展）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NtWW.1sIF5ZUfPi2L1PvQQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/e2c7ad942c1f5f7e37e58ed9414a5295\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊進入為期兩周的停火期，環球股市迎來大幅反彈，港股亦收復至25800點附近。不過，資金在此水平未見積極看好，現階段搏恒指短期能夠更上一層樓的值搏率已不大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊公佈停火兩星期以便進行和平談判後，港股周三彈高776點。雖然不排除港股或會超衝至50天平均線（現約26,142點），惟皆時部署淡倉更為有利，短線有機會調整至25,400點至25,700點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中線而言，即3至6個月的投資時長，相信恒指仍有力挑戰28,000點至30,000點的高位，故投資者若在近月低位撈貨，現時只應已先行獲利一部份的持倉，餘下持倉可待之後港股再破頂時再沽出。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-98167b62-fd83-342f-be74-c947c1d3e846-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，在3月舉行的季度研討會中分享的其中一隻利是吉利汽車（175），持續造好，創超過4年新高。投資者可部署行使價26元至27元的沽出認購期權（Short Call），但比例上應只相當於持倉的一半，以繼續留下一半持倉作長線投資，因預期吉利汽車中長線仍有望挑戰30元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一利是股奇瑞汽車（9973）表現同樣強勁，但現水平不宜高追，待調整至低於30元才考慮。至於已經持有的投資者，則可繼續持有，無須急於獲利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里（9988）近期表現相對浮沉，惟現水平具吸引力，可繼續吸納。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>陳立展（JK爸爸</strong>）<br/><strong>獨立股評人<br/>資深期權投資者</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%AB%8B%E8%B6%B3%E8%82%A1%E5%A3%87-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%80%BC%E5%8D%9A%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E9%AB%98-%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AA%E8%BD%89%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80-jk%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8-%E9%99%B3%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%95-083102683.html",
